{"tid":640230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌那星撐條濫權垃圾黑警渣滓嘅廢post都可以有成千負評","createTime":"2018-04-24T06:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T09:47:30.000Z","uid":76115,"like":17,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dcc0c71de0ad03afc5d71ee526fc0cc0bb555bb1","tid":640230,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"條偷拍痴漢係柒, 但佢做嘅野對成個社會影響係微不足道<br />\n反而條黑警懶係企下道德高地, 好可能犯撚左警例/法例都可以成班仆街垃圾港豬喺到叫好, 係危險過條痴漢返屋企玩賓周百鳩幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對示威者濫權就個個都睇到錯, 對啲你唔鐘意嘅人就話「拿警察咁先叫做到野」, 啲市民咁撚蠢班黑警想開先例擴權容乜鳩易?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf989dbe09c6d6272c49d89ba7cb0726fb035a8","tid":640230,"uid":76115,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:46:50.000Z","msg":"至去年10月高等法院頒下判詞，裁定《警隊條例》並未違憲，但確認表示除非在緊急情況下，警方須要有法庭手令才可檢查手機等電子產品內的內容，不過有關的保障並不延伸至手機本身。<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/i8q8Lu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fi8q8Lu&d=dwnxjq7AAAmXthCMTWeEytU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=12073c85\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/i8q8Lu</a><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母地鐵影下女有幾緊急呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n濫權濫到出哂面仲可以講乜野「佢個出發點係好」, 咁要法律來做乜撚野呀, 畀班盲字都唔撚識多隻嘅垃圾毅進仔做道德判官自由執法咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf01efc80ef0564834a7c9e1a8bf1140e9f0842","tid":640230,"uid":151904,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"你試下你條女比人影睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過算啦你條上網搵存在感嘅毒撚應該唔會想像到"},{"pid":"390bfcc3a52cdbf2d7e6bf53d7620ddf88197d47","tid":640230,"uid":76115,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"9cf01efc80ef0564834a7c9e1a8bf1140e9f0842","tid":640230,"uid":151904,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"你試下你條女比人影睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過算啦你條上網搵存在感嘅毒撚應該唔會想像到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:53:04.000Z","msg":"屌你老母九唔搭八, 而家講緊條黑警濫權濫到出哂面仲可以有人撐呀<br />\n<br />\n一句我好撚緊張我條女就乜權都畀哂班黑警, 你咁撚鐘意唔要法治唔要自由唔要私隱、淨係要畀人保護嘅不如去北韓住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4741fd539e9cb84d418fcadfd8b2b3090ecc337f","tid":640230,"uid":76115,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T06:59:15.000Z","msg":"你有女朋友有屌過閪所以就要大條道理支持黑警周街逼人解手機鎖? 邊個唔同意就係毒撚?<br />\n<br />\n你呢啲「point」講出來個時有無面撚紅?"},{"pid":"8f923d5ff770ff82f4abf499a7152a0b970d99a2","tid":640230,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2be56bcbe5c41fa336186641625065f0ba6044e","tid":640230,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af47f913d854506767607d007e79ea8412fe47b2","tid":640230,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:24:00.000Z","msg":"負評唔係啱咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2261187d75d3a4fabf43dfee4ea099769c2e9dc1","tid":640230,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af47f913d854506767607d007e79ea8412fe47b2","tid":640230,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:24:00.000Z","msg":"負評唔係啱咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T07:24:56.000Z","msg":"打錯<br />\n屌那星撐條濫權垃圾黑警渣滓嘅廢post都可以有成千<del>負</del>正評"},{"pid":"bb56b13f6e89dde4713120726a8104e4c7bd1f0a","tid":640230,"uid":57488,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2261187d75d3a4fabf43dfee4ea099769c2e9dc1","tid":640230,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af47f913d854506767607d007e79ea8412fe47b2","tid":640230,"uid":57488,"like":0,"disl